  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Impact of a 4-week exercise intervention vs. a stress-management-training on physical
      activity (measured objectively and by questionnaire) of cancer patients of different entities
      and out-patient regimes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
